Spec: SpecDD Version Service
Purpose:
  Validate and compare SpecDD release version strings.

Structure:
  ./specdd-version.ts: SpecDD version service implementation.
  ./specdd-version.test.ts: SpecDD version service tests.

Owns:
  ./specdd-version.ts
  ./specdd-version.test.ts

References:
  /src/constants.sdd

Must:
  Accept dotted numeric versions such as 1.2 or 1.2.3.
  Reject versions with a leading v.
  Provide a numeric suggestion when a rejected version has a leading v.
  Compare versions numerically, treating missing parts as zero.

Must not:
  Read files.
  Perform network operations.

Exposes:
  @SpecDDVersion
  @SpecDDVersion.isValid
  @SpecDDVersion.suggest
  @SpecDDVersion.validate
  @SpecDDVersion.compare

Raises:
  @SpecDDInvalidVersionError
